README for Class::Accessor::Lvalue 0.01

=head1 NAME

Class::Accessor::Lvalue - create Lvalue accessors


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

This module has external dependencies on the following modules:

 Class::Accessor
 Want

=head1 INSTALLATION

 perl Build.PL
 perl Build test

and if all goes well

 perl Build install

